<L>__{interior l.a. county jail police cell day}
<A>__{viktor sits in his cell, arms crossed, quietly seething, while his lawyer lays out his trial strategy.}
<C>__{lawyer}
<P>__{(hushed tones, referring}
<D>__{to a thick psychiatric}
<P>__{report)}
<D>__{... listen, i've found a psychiatrist in ventura well respected who's willing to testify under oath that you have diminished capacity due to the trauma of your divorce, ten years of abject failure in the movie business and a bump on the head you sustained as a child }
<A>__{viktor, fuming throughout this, suddenly explodes.}
<C>__{viktor}
<D>__{ no! i can't go along with this horseshit! just tell them they can fry me!}
<C>__{lawyer}
<P>__{(aghast, looking around to see if anyone has heard)}
<D>__{what?!}
